snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [140] Famicom Mini: Balloon Fight
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Another endless game. It loops random levels after a while, I played it until level 25. Also there is a Balloon Trip mode, where I played it until I reached rank 1. That's all there is to it. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
